ActPhysical Activity and Sport Act
PrecisOrder designating, for the purposes of this Act, (a) the MINISTER OF HEALTH as the Minister in respect of physical activity, and (b) the MINISTER OF CANADIAN HERITAGE in respect of sport, effective June 15, 2003.
